**Trueplace: Supercharging Your Interview Game**

Founded in 2021, Trueplace is a San Francisco-based startup on a mission to empower professionals in their interview processes. The company's core offering? An AI-driven tool designed to enhance interview performance and help users present their best selves. They made quite a mark during their time in Y Combinator's W22 batch, signaling their innovative approach and potential for growth.

Despite their lean team of just two employees, Trueplace is making waves in the artificial intelligence space, specifically within the San Francisco Bay Area. Their product is still under wraps, operating in stealth mode, but you can bet that when it’s fully unveiled, it will bring a fresh perspective to interview preparation.

With a focus on supercharging professionals, Trueplace is geared towards revolutionizing the way candidates prepare for interviews, making them more confident and polished than ever before. Their tagline says it succinctly: they want to supercharge your interviews.

If you want to keep an eye on their journey or dive deeper into what they’re working on, check out their website: [Trueplace](https://www.trueplace.ca/).
